---
title: Tandoori-Style Chicken with Grilled Naan and Cucumber-Tomato Salad
description: Tender chicken gets a quick marinade in tikka sauce before grilling adds flavour reminiscent of a blazing hot tandoor oven. Golden naan completes this delicious meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-style-tandoori-dcb2d58b.jpg
